{"type": "article", "id": 15988, "title": "可生火的工具“E.R.A”", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000335um2l3RMUtAN0JQqk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可以用来生火煮食物的“E.R.A”（Emergency Relief Assistance），打开缠绕在外的束带，取出上面倒扣的炉子和下面的锅就可以用任何燃料生火了。炉子外还加了防风罩，能将锅盆固定起来。而一些必备的小工具如指南针、手电筒、小刀和急救包等都能放在中间，方便携带。适合户外野餐或者灾难来临时的不时之需。<a href=\"http://www.akifkurtulus.com/#1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143426As7t1lYzeWwF8kEf.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143426bzAVoRPUeW0kf738.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434273yYBqIHcpkhXFTSx.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143427szix0rEqFXL5fSWH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143428bSlxjZI9t4Dnw2YT.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}